correctness.rationale: Multiple critical inaccuracies and unsupported placeholders are present despite some core items being correct. Correct items: PEALD for In2O3/Ga2O3/ZnO, Ar carrier/purging gas, O2 plasma (100 W), deposition T=200 °C, P≈1.2 Torr, IGZO supercycle ratio 6:1:1, amorphous phase, device metrics (μFE=27.6 cm2/Vs, VTH=0.05 V, SS=61 mV/dec). Major issues: (1) Dosing/purge times are taken from Al2O3 GI ALD (TMA/O3) and misapplied to IGZO sub-cycles, and units are wrong (seconds in article vs milliseconds in JSON): TMA dose 0.1 s, purge 25 s, O3 dose 5 s, purge 20 s are not for IGZO and were entered as 0.1 ms/25 ms/5 ms/20 ms. (2) Growth per cycle (0.9 Å) was reported for Al2O3 (Figure S5), not for In2O3, Ga2O3, ZnO; assigning 0.9 Å to all sub-oxides is unsupported. (3) numberofCycles=8 conflates thickness (8 nm) with cycles; total IGZO cycles were not reported and 8 cycles is inconsistent with 8 nm at ~Å/cycle. (4) Resistivity is incorrect: 1.34 was a conductivity in S/cm after 600 °C anneal; reporting 1.34 Ω·m is wrong quantity and value (should be ~0.0075 Ω·m if using that σ). (5) Optical refractive index 1.62 and film density 3.12 g/cm3 belong to Al2O3 GI, not IGZO; misassigned to IGZO materialProperties. (6) Many placeholders not traceable to the article: flowRates set to 0, uniformity variation=0%, conformality aspect ratio=0, nucleationPeriod=0, saturation=True without evidence, deliveryMethod="not specified", elementalConcentration value=0%, onOffRatio=0. (7) materialProperties.electricalProperties.mobility uses device field-effect mobility (should be left out or replaced by film (e.g., Hall) data if provided). (8) The process conflates two distinct ALD processes (IGZO active layer and Al2O3 gate insulator); these should be represented as separate processes to maintain semantic coherence and traceability. Corrections needed: remove/replace GI-specific parameters under IGZO process; provide only IGZO-specific dosing/purge/growth data (or omit optional fields when schema allows); fix units for times if reported; correct resistivity vs conductivity; remove zero/placeholder values; restrict optical and density values to the correct material; split into two processes (IGZO PEALD and Al2O3 ALD) with their own parameters.

completeness.rationale: The extraction is largely incomplete and contains numerous incorrect or non-traceable values, plus schema issues. Key problems: (1) Multiple processes not captured: the article reports two distinct ALD processes (IGZO PEALD active layer; Al2O3 GI ALD with TMA/O3 at 200–400 °C, 350 mTorr, cycle timing). Only one process is provided, and parts of the GI process are incorrectly mixed into the IGZO process. A separate Al2O3 process instance is required. (2) Dosing/purge times and GPC misattributed and unit errors: 0.1 s TMA dose/25 s purge/5 s O3/20 s purge are for Al2O3 GI, not for In2O3/Ga2O3/ZnO cycles. They are also entered in milliseconds (MilliSEC) without conversion (e.g., 5 s should be 5000 ms), making them off by ~1000×. GPC 0.9 Å/cycle pertains to Al2O3, not IGZO sub-cycles; no IGZO GPC is reported. (3) Unsupported placeholder zeros: flowRates (all 0.0 sccm), carrierDensity (0), uniformity variation (0%), conformality aspect ratio (0), elemental concentration value (0%), onOffRatio (0), roughness (0 nm), nucleationPeriod (0) are not in the article and are not traceable. (4) Incorrect values: numberofCycles set to 8 (the article does not report total ALD cycles; 8 nm is the film thickness, not cycle count). Resistivity is wrong: article gives conductivity 1.34 S/cm (after 600 °C); correct resistivity ≈ 0.0075 Ω·m, not 1.34 Ω·m. Film density (3.12 g/cm3) and refractive index (1.62) are for Al2O3 (GI), not IGZO; they are misassigned to the IGZO film. (5) Schema/structural issues: thicknessControl.numberofCycles is incorrectly nested under growthPerCycle; filmThickness appears duplicated/misplaced; many required fields are filled with non-credible values to satisfy the schema. (6) Partial correctness: PEALD method, precursors (DADI/TMGa/DEZ), O2 plasma (100 W), deposition temperature (200 °C), pressure (1.2 Torr), substrate, supercycle ratio (6:1:1), cation ratio (In0.52:Ga0.18:Zn0.30), device metrics (μFE 27.6 cm2/Vs, VTH 0.05 V, SS 61 mV/dec) align with the article. To improve: add a separate Al2O3 ALD process; remove/replace all placeholder zeros with only reported values; correct dosing/purge timings and units or omit if not reported; correct resistivity; remove Al2O3 properties from IGZO materialProperties; provide only traceable values (e.g., composition ratio, amorphous phase) and leave schema fields that cannot be supported unfilled in a compliant manner.
